pr_title: Fix #130 Refactor login
pr_body:
Fix #130 

Changes made in the login: 

- Now endpoints in BaseURL.kt just need to be changed in order to use a different endpoint. 
- Instead of using kttp, I'm now using okhttp and retrofit to sign in
- Credentials are saved, user need not login everytime the app is opened. 
- UI enhancements: Using TextInputLayout and displaying errors under the edit text itself instead of showing toast. 
- Using rxjava for dependency injection for the login part
- Numerous other minor improvements 

I have added the idea files as well since I rewrote the app from scratch for proper login and then integrated the existing files with the new ones.
